  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0da7\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dc2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0daf \u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One lakh tons of diesel will arrive today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Ministry of Energy said that a ship with one lakh metric tons of auto diesel and super diesel is scheduled to arrive in Colombo today (17) and the shortage of super diesel in the country will end accordingly.",
        "The officer further said that this super diesel stock was received after more than two months and after the completion of the tests of the diesel stock, it will be gradually released to the filling station."
      ],
